                    It doesn't look like anyone from the UK has purchased one of these. So I decided to be the first. It's actually quite useful with a little tweaking. I would suggest using Google Chrome instead of the default browser. The camera is surprisingly good considering the overall cost of the phone. The flashlight is very handy too. Overall, I think it makes a great backup phone. I bring it to work but don't use it so often.
